how to build a maven project?

  steps file-->new--other--maven--maven project-->next
  -->create simple project-->use default location-->
  --Group Id--Artifact ID--Finish.
  Then update propertise file if needed
  <properties>
    <maven.compiler.target>17</maven.compiler.target>
    <maven.compiler.source>17</maven.compiler.source>
   </properties>
   
   
   what is pom.xml file?
     it is configuration file for the project
   
   what is artifactId ?
   is the project name
   
   what is the groupId ?
   package name
   
